cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO 

The paper deals with depth-based recognition methods using 3D CAD models, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) for unsupervised learning also suggests a possible connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the application of the proposed approach to various recognition methods suggests a possible connection to robotics (cs.RO).
